Maga
====


A DHT crawler framework using asyncio.


Usage
-----
.. code-block:: python

    from maga import Maga

    import logging
    logging.basicConfig(level=logging.INFO)


    class Crawler(Maga):
        async def handler(self, infohash):
            logging.info(infohash)

    crawler = Crawler()
    crawler.run(6881)



